      <title>中国愿意改善与印度的关系，解决边界争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/china-willing-to-improve-ties-with-india-work-on-border-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示愿意与印度共同努力改善关系，并表示两国边界争端“应得到妥善处理”，这是印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪以微弱优势赢得第三任期后两国间的最新交流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/china-willing-to-improve-ties-with-india-work-on-border-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:47:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统选举临近，执政联盟谈判陷入僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/south-african-elections-coalition-talks-drag-on-as-presidential-vote-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距南非议会召开选举新总统仅剩两天，新政府的组成仍不明朗，主要政党之间的联盟谈判尚未最终确定。]]></description>
